Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, February 2 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The 
Presidium of the Mongolian Democratic Union made a statement, 
addressing its members and supporters. 
  In the statement it is noted that abuse of power and bribery 
are widely spreading in the country among a state and government 
high officials, reaching the level capable to cause a threat to 
the national security. In this connection the Mongolian 
Democratic Union announces about its intention to liven up its 
political activity. 

